text: The Renault R 312 is a bus produced by Renault. It replaced the SC 10 in 1987, and was replaced by the Irisbus Agora in 1996. == Engines == * 9.8 litre straight-6 turbodiesel, 152 kW (207 hp) * 9.8 litre straight-6 turbodiesel, 187 kW (254 hp) R 312 Category:1980s automobiles Category:1990s automobiles
